item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

[quote=“Telenim, post:2, topic:299378”]I’m sure it has something to do with when you click the prayer icon then?..

Search the button ID and find out if it activates the headicon and find out what the actual headicon IDs are and change it, or something like that, I haven’t really done anything with Runescape Private Servers lately.[/quote]
Yea i hate to say it, i made a command to change headicons on command. There are 127 head-icons. About 120 of those runescape has never used, and probably not seen until that time. Up at the ID 128 the entire sequence starts over again, i know this because i kept going until 300. Took me about hour and a half to get all of those down ROFL. I might release, just havent had the motivation to.
